Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:02.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:07.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:14.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:56.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:02.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:02.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:07.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:14.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:56.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:02.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:08.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架敵機正向本艦靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火  他們攻過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在做什麼  開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了人的話  我就跟你們一樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！ 趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的話  又會傷害到無辜的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也是你們的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝得太靠前了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準尉  拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣不下扳機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  你已經盡力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不盡全力  還是在侮辱我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  我是阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam  由我送你上路！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我就在等你出這殺手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟如此之強…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再放手了  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過載？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…機體居然沒準備萬全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒有揮刀的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  各機包圍雙爐機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體Gundam退後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·諾瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要切斷敵軍的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魚雷發散高濃度粒子和煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  煙霧太大…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子通信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交戰空域出現煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子量增大  與MS隊的通訊中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在才改變戰術？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整姿勢  發出撤退指令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉不到Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說沒有Arios的反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用任務記錄確定Arios的交戰空域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把OO收容之後  使用Seravee和Cherudim對Arios進行搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說你也太擅自做主了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不想聽你廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲中尉的AHEAD失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即組織搜索隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要怎麼向斯密爾諾夫上校交代…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎沒有追兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們拖住了A-LAWS嗎  Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪麗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付廢物一個的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  瑪麗·帕法西！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里…路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  你記得我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里…路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·帕法西！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  無論如何也不用勞您大駕親自出擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據記錄應該是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦量子波是這樣感覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內心在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的事也是這樣  全是Gundam造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸艦…命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終止對中尉的搜索？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上層的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隊專注於Celestial Being的戰鬥即可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索中尉的任務就交給正規軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim  已發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  到達彈射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞  已經把Arios的交戰空域位置傳給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘量避免與A-LAWS交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專注於搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  已發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上進行潛航準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  叫你別用TRANS-AM了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓Twin-Drive能正常運轉都很勉強的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你修好它  阿里路亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  讓你來修理Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到卡塔隆的成員們安然撤退為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼我都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查看了一下機體  兩台的系統都無法啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大概是修不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人來救援就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何你會成了蘇摩·佩麗絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是通過植入不同的人格  以復原我失去的五感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關借由將我作為超兵送到軍隊  企圖保存組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正因為這樣  我才得以看得到你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就認出是你了  是因為腦量子波嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想過能和你直接交談…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我嗎  你逃出超人機關後怎麼樣了？  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想逃脫機關的處分  就和同伴一起逃離了設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我還為沒帶你一起走而後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那反而還比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和同伴搶了艘運送艦逃離了殖民衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  漫無目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們持續著漂流  直到艦內的食物和氧氣消耗殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不想死  阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就得死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的  在你體內還存在著另一個人格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想找藉口  哈利路亞就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一存活下來的我詛咒著命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒著超人機關和這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我為改變世界而成為Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為超兵能做的  也就只有戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  你有作為蘇摩·佩麗絲時候的記憶嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  我也記得她的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你應該也知道吧  我做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他們  用這雙手將同伴和同胞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次奪走了大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣  我也曾殺死過你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那時候的攻擊  我將另一個你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將哈利路亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我刻上了這道傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  那是蘇摩·佩麗絲做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣  佩麗絲就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  對不起  我該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣的  在我知道蘇摩·佩麗絲就是瑪麗之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只想著你了  想著要救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在救出你之後  我該怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我  根本沒有什麼能為你做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能在身邊我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我遇到你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對失去五感只能用腦量子波叫喊的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出反應的人就只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有你  我才能感謝自己活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看著這樣的你  能跟你交談甚至觸摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這一刻竟能到來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊  我感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎  所有人集中到中央區域去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕男子的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  你就是那時候的Gundam機師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開中尉  Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了啊  克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  第三支部被敵人摧毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就為能再會而高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個  聯邦政府終於來奪取中東了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍侵入被攻擊的阿扎迪斯坦  建立了臨時政府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時政府…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  阿扎迪斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府以臨時政府為中心將各國解體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備重新編制中東
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解體  中東的重新編制…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  恐怕阿扎迪斯坦王國已不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…阿扎迪斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格被覆蓋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  現在的我不是蘇摩·佩麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗…瑪麗·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗  這就是中尉真正的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關竟然做過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗是個溫柔的女孩子  她是不會殺人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把瑪麗交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是回到聯邦或A-LAWS的話  又會被當成超兵使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是Celestial Being  中尉跟你在一起又會被捲進戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會這樣做的  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒蠢到會相信恐怖分子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為你…不對  是你們的愚蠢行動  失去了很多同胞和部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這仇恨我可沒忘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣  上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換  請你發誓再也不將瑪麗…\N不  再也不將蘇摩·佩麗絲捲入鬥爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  瑪麗  只要你能幸福就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才  蘇摩·佩麗絲中尉光榮戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將向上層報告  就此返航  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我還沒向你道謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你參加五年前固定軌道站事故的救援行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇摩·佩麗絲很感謝您\N只徵用她參加對Gundam戰且沒讓她參加其它作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種說話方式  你的確不是我所認識的中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  我體內的蘇摩·佩麗絲這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我曾想成為您的女兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  有這一句話就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去  你要繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起幸福地活下去
